snippet.title: The Uzujigoku Massacre - Demo : Genesis Playthrough [No Commentary]
snippet.description:
✝✝✝

The Uzujigoku Massacre's Official Demo Full Playthrough made with DREditor.

✝✝✝

The Uzujigoku Massacre is a Danganronpa fan project that has no affiliation with Spike Chunsoft. All assets are originally created and privately owned. We do not intend on making any sort of monetization from this project, nor spend any money in the development of this project. Please support The Uzujigoku Massacre and the official release of the official Danganronpa series.

✝✝✝

Takiyo Mochizuki is accepted into Heaven’s Bridge Boarding School, Japan’s most elite academy. Renowned for molding talented individuals into Ultimates - skilled professionals in their desired fields - Heaven’s Bridge accepts students between 10-20 in its pursuit of notable alumni destined to make their mark on Japanese history. 
After an unfortunate tragedy forced the school into a temporary shutdown some years ago, it has now reopened, and intends to restart its prestigious legacy with its 21st class.
Unbeknownst to them, another tragedy is quickly approaching.

✝✝✝

Please support us by following our Twitter, UzuMassacre, and joining our discord server.

✝✝✝
